1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,830
***

2
00:00:02,039 --> 00:00:04,139
Daddy, I know you don't want me
to do this.

3
00:00:04,540 --> 00:00:06,930
I just want you to know,
I'm not going to let you down.

4
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:09,710
Kate Butler... parents reported
her missing three years ago.

5
00:00:09,750 --> 00:00:11,680
Pennsylvania Military Institute.

6
00:00:11,760 --> 00:00:13,590
I knew the cadets hated her.

7
00:00:13,910 --> 00:00:14,710
Rhianna ?

8
00:00:14,790 --> 00:00:16,610
That's what they called Ryan
after Kate smoked him.

9
00:00:16,690 --> 00:00:19,680
Look,it wasn't... the students
that Kate Butler had to worry about.

10
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:21,170
Cadet Gardner here
will show you to Moe.

11
00:00:21,230 --> 00:00:22,890
He's my operations officer.

12
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,350
Look, I'd be lying to you to say

13
00:00:24,351 --> 00:00:26,651
that there wasn't resentment
among some of the cadets.

14
00:00:26,810 --> 00:00:28,720
- Lawrence !
- Yes, Major.

15
00:00:30,780 --> 00:00:32,670
Come on, Scotty. Pick up.

16
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:47,840
....................

17
00:01:04,780 --> 00:01:08,620
