00:16:20,290 --> 00:16:22,680
<i>"Nothingman" by Pearl Jam</i>

285
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:24,690
Attention to orders.

286
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:28,290
As First Sergeant, Echo Company,
I'd like to present

287
00:16:28,330 --> 00:16:31,170
the PMI Distinction Medal to
a fourth class cadet

288
00:16:31,171 --> 00:16:32,971
