289
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:37,840
Cadet Butler, front and center.

290
00:16:41,450 --> 00:16:42,780
Sir.

291
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:44,870
Cadet Butler, you have displayed
outstanding qualities

292
00:16:44,871 --> 00:16:47,771
in both academics
and physical training.

293
00:16:49,530 --> 00:16:50,750
Thank you, sir.

294
00:16:50,830 --> 00:16:52,750
Do you have anything to say ?

295
00:16:53,810 --> 00:16:55,770
Yes, I do, sir.

296
00:16:55,900 --> 00:16:57,550
Stand at ease.

297
00:16:59,550 --> 00:17:03,990
"What we obtain too cheap,
we esteem too lightly.

298
00:17:04,060 --> 00:17:07,600
" 'Tis dearness only that
gives everything its value.

299
00:17:07,910 --> 00:17:09,820
I didn't understand why
First Sergeant Addison

300
00:17:09,821 --> 00:17:11,921
was quoting Thomas Paine
our first day here.

301
00:17:13,210 --> 00:17:14,570
But I do now.

302
00:17:15,277 --> 00:17:18,366
We might not fighting the
american revolution like he was,

303
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,590
but we're still fighting.

304
00:17:20,630 --> 00:17:22,430
Fighting for the strength
to keep at it,

305
00:17:22,731 --> 00:17:25,531
fighting for the respect
of our company,

306
00:17:26,590 --> 00:17:28,780
and for the pride of our families.

307
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:35,670
I hope to earn them all someday.

308
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:42,420
Echo Company, atten-hut !

309
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:50,420
I remember the first day
she was born.

310
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:54,200
Those tiny little hands,
they had such a tight grip,

311
00:17:54,201 --> 00:17:56,501
like she'd never let go.

312
00:17:57,280 --> 00:18:00,130
Three hours is long time
to spend in a chapel.

313
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,740
Sure you didn't go anywhere
else that night, Hank ?

314
00:18:01,770 --> 00:18:04,370
I didn't go looking for those cadets.

315
00:18:04,490 --> 00:18:08,020
I left the list that Murillo
gave me on his secretary's desk.

316
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:11,400
Going to be checking with her on that.

317
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:14,900
Was the last chance I had
to tell her how proud I was.

318
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:18,700
And I walked away.

319
00:18:22,780 --> 00:18:26,080
Got the Bucks County Coroner's
report on Cadet Lawrence Gardner.

320
00:18:26,550 --> 00:18:28,980
Cause of death, manual strangulation.

321
00:18:29,020 --> 00:18:31,810
And no scrapings under his
nails,no bruises or cuts.

322
00:18:31,890 --> 00:18:32,870
Kid didn't put up a fight.

323
00:18:32,980 --> 00:18:35,100
Or it happened so fast,
he didn't have time to wake up.

324
00:18:35,150 --> 00:18:37,230
Chaplain said Lawrence
helped out with the services.

325
