I want to know who was.

329
00:18:48,470 --> 00:18:50,360
CSU found something
in Kate's quarters

330
00:18:50,361 --> 00:18:52,561
where Lawrence's body
was found.

331
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:58,320
A letter to Kate.

332
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:01,190
