00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:27,300
Come on, Ryan. We can help you.

474
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:30,080
Nobody's gonna help me.

475
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:32,950
Look, I can't go to jail.
Nobody's gonna bail me out.

476
00:27:33,020 --> 00:27:35,950
Bad shape.Bad shape.

477
00:27:38,780 --> 00:27:39,200
Gun !

478
00:27:39,210 --> 00:27:41,980
You come any closer, I swear
to God, I'm gonna shoot.

479
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:44,660
You don't have to worry about that.I'm
