486
00:28:13,780 --> 00:28:16,880
That Saturday night ?
November 15, 2005 ?

487
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,890
Every Saturday night.

488
00:28:18,970 --> 00:28:21,010
You know, it was just me.

489
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:23,560
Kate was there, too ?

490
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:26,000
The only other cadet around.

491
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:30,000
And even with all the crap
that she took, she was a girl.

492
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:32,240
And they still liked her
better than me.

493
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:36,220
<i>"Release" by Pearl Jam.</i>

494
00:28:43,650 --> 00:28:45,770
