497
00:28:50,060 --> 00:28:51,780
I heard you are a good tutor, so...

498
00:28:51,781 --> 00:28:52,981
I haven't even looked at it yet.

499
00:28:53,060 --> 00:28:56,240
Oh,I just figured you'd probably
be holed up studying, too, so...

500
00:28:56,330 --> 00:28:58,170
You're not going out ?

501
00:28:58,410 --> 00:28:59,670
No.

502
00:28:59,710 --> 00:29:02,780
What's new ? I guess we
have that in common, huh ?

503
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,170
Why don't you take my notes ?

504
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,650
Okay, cool.

505
00:29:16,970 --> 00:29:17,990
So, what are you...?

506
00:29:18,070 --> 00:29:19,910
What's up ? Are you just...?
Are you just going to bed ?

