00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:29,710
Meeting some of the guys.

510
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:32,130
You're kidding.

511
00:29:32,250 --> 00:29:33,540
Who ?

512
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:35,660
Echo Company ?

513
00:29:37,740 --> 00:29:40,020
