of the body ?

537
00:31:09,710 --> 00:31:11,600
Somebody helped him.

538
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,440
Lawrence ?

539
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:16,740
Kid doesn't have it in him to
pull off a premeditated murder.

540
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:20,000
And why confess to one murder,
but not two ?

541
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:22,920
The Suburban from PMI
that hit you

