00:31:22,921 --> 00:31:25,921
was ticketed five times
in the past four years.

543
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:29,100
95 South, 76 West
and Ridge Avenue.

544
00:31:29,140 --> 00:31:31,110
On the way to Roxborough.

545
00:31:31,170 --> 00:31:33,880
Same driver used the car every time.

546
00:31:34,970 --> 00:31:36,510
Army.

547
00:31:36,590 --> 00:31:40,450
Rangers, right ?Got to be a tough
son of a bitch to wear that beret.

548
00:31:40,530 --> 00:31:44,650
Came back to PMI in
'87 as a PT instructor.

549
00:31:44,730 --> 00:31:46,700
You're an institution.

550
00:31:46,740 --> 00:31:49,210
Part of the long blue line.

551
00:31:49,290 --> 00:31:52,350
Fourth generation... sir.

552
00:31:54,160 --> 00:31:57,060
Been looking over Ryan
Stewart's transcript.

553
00:31:57,140 --> 00:32:00,750
Uh, academic...  probation twice.

554
00:32:00,830 --> 00:32:04,480
Poor to failing marks in...

555
00:32:06,781 --> 00:32:07,781
...PT.

556
00:32:08,250 --> 00:32:10,250
Ma'am ?

557
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:13,980
