709
00:42:18,450 --> 00:42:20,460
<i>I've missed so much of your life.</i>

710
00:42:20,530 --> 00:42:23,200
<i>For that, I am sorry.</i>

711
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:24,400
<i>Not only to you,</i>

712
00:42:24,401 --> 00:42:29,401
<i>but for depriving myself for
all those times you needed a father,</i>

713
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:32,620
<i>somebody to protect you.</i>

714
00:42:33,610 --> 00:42:38,700
* And now my bitter hands
Cradle broken glass *

715
00:42:38,700 --> 00:42:42,610
<i>When you showed up that day at
the park all these years later,</i>

716
00:42:42,690 --> 00:42:44,890
<i>my heart about jumped out
of my chest.</i>

717
00:42:44,930 --> 00:42:46,750
<i>I thought maybe you came
to judge me</i>

718
00:42:46,751 --> 00:42:47,951
<i>till I realized</i>

719
00:42:48,030 --> 00:42:51,010
<i>I'm the only parent you got left.</i>

720
00:42:51,090 --> 00:42:54,610
<i>Like it or not,
you only get one father.</i>

721
00:42:54,730 --> 00:42:58,380
* Gone bad Turned my world
to black *

722
00:42:58,381 --> 00:43:01,481
* Tattooed all I see *

723
00:43:01,710 --> 00:43:08,190
* All that I am All I'll be...*

724
00:43:15,920 --> 00:43:21,150
<i>Just know, if there's ever another moment
in your life when you need me,</i>

